      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'll stick to the ibuprofen for now. it's just that the pain is kind of throbbing and it hurts way more when i walk or even just move in bed. feels more intense than usual cramps though. do u think it's worth going to the doctor tonight or should i just wait and see if it settles down by morning? im just worried about the cost of an ER visit if its nothing.",
