      "content": "a warm compress sounds good, i'll try that. i'm just so tired and i really don't want to deal with a hospital at 2am if it's just gas. if i take a couple of the ibuprofen now, it should hopefully numb the pain enough so i can sleep through the night, right? i'll just monitor it in the morning. if i take a slightly higher dose like 800mg it won't hurt anything, right? i just really need to sleep.",
